{"tid":861284,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【駭人慎入】15cm蟲眼球內遊走 醫生活生生咁抆返出嚟","createTime":"2018-10-14T04:20:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T16:13:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ba447e5256c615f3b1a12a4d73e349d8d0d52642","tid":861284,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"印度一名老翁的眼球內，藏有一條15厘米長的寄生蟲，而且還可以游動，噁心非常。<br />\n眼內生蟲的是卡納塔克邦（Karnataka）一名60歲男子，他因眼睛又痛又癢求診，片段拍到他的右眼眼白有一條長長的寄生蟲，「打蛇餅」地盤在一角。<br />\n醫生謝蒂（Srikanth Shetty）立刻動手術，小心翼翼開傷口用鉗拉出整條寄生蟲，原來寄生蟲足足有15厘米長。謝蒂表示難度在於完整拉出整條活蟲，殺死牠的話可能引起其他併發症，「活蟲在游動，很難鉗起牠。」<br />\n但驚嚇還未完結，醫生其後更在他的血液內發現有蟲，需要服藥治理。男子表示並不知道為何及何時起體內有寄生蟲。<br />\n謝蒂指該蟲應是班氏絲蟲（Wuchereria Bancrofti），通常經蚊叮傳播，病例不算罕有，估計中非、南美及中美等地有1.2億人感染班氏絲蟲，不過長在眼裡屬少見。他稱如不及時處理，可對眼睛造成永久性傷害。<br />\n英國《每日郵報》<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181013/large/1539411057_ce0e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181013%2Flarge%2F1539411057_ce0e.jpg&h=117da6e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181013/large/1539411106_9dae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181013%2Flarge%2F1539411106_9dae.jpg&h=e1497149&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181013/large/1539411106_6855.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181013%2Flarge%2F1539411106_6855.jpg&h=ab0100f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nlink入面有片<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181014/58790008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F58790008&d=hHFbq%2F4vxrP6tvKf92iQmwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=822702f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181014%2F58790008&h=49fe2f6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181014/58790008</a>"},{"pid":"f3454f7196051b2628d2deb34594fb84eabed385","tid":861284,"uid":201732,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T04:22:06.000Z","msg":"睇住佢炆出黎果下好治癒"},{"pid":"d19401f7e5677f739720d204e6aeace7bf162ae6","tid":861284,"uid":180165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"好似痴住啲米線喺上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a77eb62be77b04ebba3f5c30ac047d95246f92","tid":861284,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19401f7e5677f739720d204e6aeace7bf162ae6","tid":861284,"uid":180165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"好似痴住啲米線喺上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T06:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b147a6d9172ed073a15b35944b3088bfd0be4109","tid":861284,"uid":57927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d19401f7e5677f739720d204e6aeace7bf162ae6","tid":861284,"uid":180165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T04:23:40.000Z","msg":"好似痴住啲米線喺上面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T13:36:14.000Z","msg":"想一啖啜出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff02f32fca01491388ec08ffc4875c4d6d8d99aa","tid":861284,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T14:33:59.000Z","msg":"核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"202657647735ea49691226195236434d974db3b9","tid":861284,"u